{"tid":953511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(貢獻蛆國)  傳TVB擬「加大力度」溝貨救債仔星美","createTime":"2018-12-24T03:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T12:16:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"80feaa3abb0a2c42fa9fa8096a458288b797d334","tid":953511,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"已停牌三個月的內地戲線營運商星美控股(00198)，疑因擴張過快致資金斷鏈。據報指，電視廣播(TVB)(00511)覬覦星美院線資產，擬做「白武士」出手救星美，TVB更為此事成立獨立委員會處理，董事會亦就星美重組進行討論。<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》報道指，星美控股旗下320家戲院中已有逾四成停運，去年度欠債估計約50億元，而TVB一直有意北上大展拳腳，延續其影視王國，因此視星美為一個「千載難逢」的機會，以打入內地影院市場。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，TVB已成立由非執董組成的獨立委員會，專責星美重組計畫，並已委任德勤會計師事務所對星美進行盡職調查。德勤已於上周提交報告，而董事長周前亦曾進行討論，惟仍未有定案。<br />\n<br />\n報道提到，已有星美債權人與TVB接洽，不排除會聯同TVB一同向星美提出重組計劃。<br />\n<br />\nTVB今年向星美投資兩筆債券，分別為2,300萬美元的無抵押可贖回定息債券，以及8,300萬美元可換股債券，佔星美擴大後股本5.86%，兩債折合涉資約8.3億港元。<br />\n<br />\n星美月初通告指出，因公司缺乏足夠流動資金營運，上月欠薪1.08億元、欠租2.01億元、以及電影版權費欠1.5億元，旗下已有140家戲院停運，有11家或因欠租而無法贖回。公司亦違反部分貸款協議，未能及時償還的本金或利息，於上月底共達37.75億元。惟TVB早前回覆傳媒指，如期收到星美的派息，未出現違約情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2018/12/24/010106403.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ffinance%2Fsystem%2F2018%2F12%2F24%2F010106403.shtml&d=BOTFg90aRdpsR6jSq54p9smB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1626c192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2018/12/24/010106403.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"97200d56ca8594a2dbeec19982b81bb21ac27c79","tid":953511,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180608/photo/bkn-20180608115338955-0608_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180608125448\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180608%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180608115338955-0608_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180608125448&h=ec4eb862&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72312c42ba9b677deba1c40a9f1693298b72913b","tid":953511,"uid":107364,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T03:58:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e33a6e23af7ffe221360e46261e0b9d9797fe04","tid":953511,"uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"萬千金元賀星美<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95dd59f2d1263dffe2b20c165b70b32da2e5d1a8","tid":953511,"uid":122686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"大陸野，面果浸一個數，底果浸又一個數"},{"pid":"44b543e64fd2ab0124f1faeefa2de33db0e17f32","tid":953511,"uid":65328,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"好呀，咁tvb就可以一齊執笠"},{"pid":"9b5dbe45f46c782e4e243ad5d2a4f5ea7da0ee57","tid":953511,"uid":128417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"班高層個腦真係裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8381f9b977fbddd74aea2526ce5f6c8e5d5c3dff","tid":953511,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f32366e3110f22faf577a67fc15caf9cc2c64e","tid":953511,"uid":91633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b5dbe45f46c782e4e243ad5d2a4f5ea7da0ee57","tid":953511,"uid":128417,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"班高層個腦真係裝屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"衣家TBB亞視翻版成浸柒味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc174edbaa6c7f4c9542a577a74d2d7e42ecb85b","tid":953511,"uid":35699,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:23:11.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵黃龍德搞會計？"},{"pid":"905fc3615bbae41d4a1b3a691a4253501e4b382e","tid":953511,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:33:37.000Z","msg":